"TermsIntro" = "Please review these Terms of Use before continuing.";
"1. Acceptance of Terms" = "1. Acceptance of Terms";
"TermsAcceptanceBody" = "By accessing or using For Special You, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use the application.";
"2. Service Description" = "2. Service Description";
"TermsServiceDescriptionBody" = "For Special You is a parent-managed health tracking application designed to help caregivers record, organize, and monitor a child's health information, daily routines, therapies, medications, nutrition, symptoms, appointments, and care history.\n\nThe application may include AI-assisted features that provide estimated nutrition information, summaries, organizational tools, and general insights based on information entered by users. These features are provided for informational and support purposes only.\n\nFor Special You is intended to assist caregivers in organizing health-related information and is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any medical condition.";
"3. User Responsibilities" = "3. User Responsibilities";
"TermsUserResponsibilitiesBody" = "By using For Special You, you agree to:\n\n• Provide accurate and complete information to the best of your knowledge.\n• Maintain the security and confidentiality of your account credentials.\n• Not share your account access with unauthorized individuals.\n• Use the application in compliance with all applicable laws and regulations.\n• Not attempt to interfere with, disrupt, or compromise the functionality or security of the service.\n• Understand that you are responsible for reviewing and verifying any information entered into or generated by the application.";
"4. Medical Disclaimer" = "4. Medical Disclaimer";
"TermsMedicalDisclaimerBody" = "For Special You does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.\n\nAny information, estimates, summaries, recommendations, or insights generated by the application, including AI-assisted features, are for informational and organizational purposes only and should not be relied upon as medical advice.\n\nAlways seek the advice of a qualified physician, healthcare provider, or other medical professional regarding any questions about a child's health, medications, therapies, symptoms, or medical conditions. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking medical care because of information provided by this application.\n\nIn the event of a medical emergency, contact emergency services or a qualified healthcare provider immediately.";
"5. AI Feature Disclaimer" = "5. AI Feature Disclaimer";
"TermsAIDisclaimerBody" = "Certain features of For Special You may utilize artificial intelligence (AI) to generate estimates, summaries, nutritional information, or organizational insights.\n\nAI-generated content may be incomplete, inaccurate, or outdated and should be independently reviewed before being used for healthcare decisions. Users are solely responsible for evaluating and verifying any information provided by AI-assisted features.\n\nFor Special You makes no guarantees regarding the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of AI-generated content.";
"6. Privacy and Data" = "6. Privacy and Data";
"TermsPrivacyDataBody" = "We take reasonable measures to protect user information. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is completely secure.\n\nBy using the application, you acknowledge that information you provide may be stored and processed as necessary to operate and improve the service. Please review our Privacy Policy for additional details regarding data collection, use, and protection.";
"7. Intellectual Property" = "7. Intellectual Property";
"TermsIntellectualPropertyBody" = "All content, features, functionality, software, designs, graphics, logos, and trademarks associated with For Special You are the property of For Special You or its licensors and are protected by applicable intellectual property laws.\n\nUsers may not reproduce, distribute, modify, reverse engineer, or create derivative works from any part of the service without prior written permission.";
"8. Limitation of Liability" = "8. Limitation of Liability";
"TermsLiabilityBody" = "To the fullest extent permitted by law, For Special You, its owners, affiliates, employees, volunteers, partners, and licensors shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, consequential, special, exemplary, or punitive damages arising from or related to the use of the application.\n\nYou acknowledge that use of the service is at your own risk and that you are solely responsible for any decisions made based on information contained within or generated by the application.";
"9. Changes to Terms" = "9. Changes to Terms";
"TermsChangesBody" = "We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Use at any time. Material changes will be communicated through the application, by email, or through other reasonable means.\n\nContinued use of For Special You following any changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms of Use.";
"10. Contact Information" = "10. Contact Information";
"TermsContactBody" = "If you have questions regarding these Terms of Use, please contact us at:\n\nEmail: forspecialyoufoundation@gmail.com\n\nFor Special You Foundation";
